author: Slidebean
description:
What Elon Musk’s shifting focus means for Tesla investors.

Tesla benefited significantly from Elon Musk’s political engagement and crypto exposure in 2024.
However, his subsequent announcement that SpaceX is now his primary focus raises questions about leadership allocation and long term strategic attention.

For investors, the issue isn’t the windfall,  it’s what happens after it.

title: Elon Musk helped make Tesla $3B richer
